♫ <i>And things were simple then</i> ♫

843
01:04:29,430 --> 01:04:35,580
♫ <i>And since they've always been</i> ♫

844
01:04:35,580 --> 01:04:39,790
♫ <i>Since I've loved you</i> ♫

845
01:04:40,690 --> 01:04:45,870
♫ <i>Standing here all alone</i> ♫

846
01:04:45,870 --> 01:04:49,940
♫ <i>Trying to be seen</i> ♫

847
01:04:50,940 --> 01:05:00,450
♫ <i>Chasing whatever they might call a dream</i> ♫

848
01:05:01,240 --> 01:05:06,210
♫ <i>But you came after all</i> ♫

849
01:05:06,210 --> 01:05:10,400
